  <brief_title>Muscle Activity and Sensation During Upright Partitioned Leg Exercise in COPD</brief_title>
  <acronym>MAPLE</acronym>
  <official_title>Leg Muscle Activity and Sensation During Upright Partitioned Exercise Compared to Walking: Propulsion of a 3-wheeled Scooter by Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
