  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to determine if: the large muscles of the leg, activated during
      walking, are also active during scooting; whether scooting alters the relationship between
      leg and breathing heaviness; whether there is evidence of leg fatigue during scooting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
